		<item>
		<title>英鎊兌日圓匯率等待英國和日本的通膨數據</title>
		<link>https://www.atfx.com/zh-hant/analysis/market-news/gbpjpy-awaits-inflation-data-uk-japan</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[ATFX]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 16:00:48 +0000</pubDate>
